snippet.title: Fish Hero Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
It’s 20% off right now!: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2898650/Fish_Hero/

A physics, parkour adventure! Launch yourself up a collection of biomes to reach the summit. Compete against friends by pushing them off platforms to throw them off course. Explore a unique world as a fish out of water.
